@startuml State Chart - Login
title State Chart Diagram - Login\nSistem Prediksi Penyebaran Penyakit Menular DBD

skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor<<blue>> #dae8fc
  BorderColor<<blue>> #6c8ebf
  BackgroundColor<<yellow>> #fff2cc
  BorderColor<<yellow>> #d6b656
  BackgroundColor<<green>> #d5e8d4
  BorderColor<<green>> #82b366
  BackgroundColor<<red>> #f8cecc
  BorderColor<<red>> #b85450
}

[*] --> HalamanLogin

state "Halaman Login Ditampilkan" as HalamanLogin <<blue>> {
}
HalamanLogin : entry / render halaman login
HalamanLogin : do / menunggu input pengguna

state "Mengisi Form Login" as MengisiForm <<blue>> {
}
MengisiForm : entry / form aktif menerima input
MengisiForm : do / input username dan password

state "Memvalidasi Kredensial" as Validasi <<yellow>> {
}
Validasi : entry / kirim data login ke server
Validasi : do / query user di database,
Validasi :       check_password_hash()

state "Login Gagal" as LoginGagal <<red>> {
}
LoginGagal : entry / tampilkan pesan error
LoginGagal : do / menunggu input ulang

state "Set Session & Update Last Login" as SetSession <<green>> {
}
SetSession : entry / login_user(user)
SetSession : do / update last_login timestamp,
SetSession :       log aktivitas ke database

state "Redirect ke Dashboard" as Dashboard <<green>> {
}
Dashboard : entry / redirect('/dashboard')
Dashboard : do / tampilkan halaman utama
Dashboard :       sesuai role pengguna

HalamanLogin --> MengisiForm : klik form input
MengisiForm --> Validasi : klik tombol Login
Validasi --> LoginGagal : [password tidak valid /\nuser tidak ditemukan]
Validasi --> SetSession : [password valid &\nuser aktif]
LoginGagal --> MengisiForm : input ulang
SetSession --> Dashboard : session aktif
Dashboard --> [*] : login berhasil

note right of Validasi
  Aktor: Pengguna (Admin / Petugas / Pimpinan)
  Objek: Login Page → Auth Controller → Database
end note

@enduml
